ModMetaData.name: Zeta Reticulans
ModMetaData.author: GarbageDayIsHereToStay
ModMetaData.description: (Newest patch notes on workshop; Version: 22-06-2020) \nCold and mechanical Zeta Reticulans are unaffected by most human-like emotions. Their frustrations mostly stem from whether work standards are being kept and mission guidelines followed; Their greatest joy is working in their field of expertise.
